data.description: Family home located in Northern Troup County!  This home features a foyer entrance that leads into a large family room with large windows, a vaulted ceiling, and a beautiful double sided fireplace with gas logs that opens to the kitchen and breakfast room. The formal dining room is situated perfectly for family dinners together.  The primary bedroom along with 2 other bedrooms are all located on the main floor, along with an office/study. The primary bedroom features include trey ceilings and an ensuite bath with a soaking tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet.  Upstairs you will find a large bonus room with a closet, that could easily be a home gym, a playroom, a sewing/crafting room, or a home office, along with a full bath for convenience.  Just outside in the fenced backyard is a swimming pool with a new, custom cover and a gazebo for those hot Summer days.  This home has so much potential for a growing family!
